1. DERIVED WORKS

   "Bistro-Demo-Tweaked" is based on:
   "Lumberyard Bistro Reference Scene"
     Source: https://github.com/godotengine/godot/issues/74965
     Author: Logan Preshaw (https://github.com/WickedInsignia)
     License: CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
   
   "Lumberyard Bistro Reference Scene" is ported from:
   "Amazon Lumberyard Bistro"
     Source: https://developer.nvidia.com/orca/amazon-lumberyard-bistro
     Author: Amazon Lumberyard (https://aws.amazon.com/lumberyard/)
     License: CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)

